%20Tyson%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20NDTV%20Thursday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20recover%20she%2C%20and%20fellow%20astronaut%20Butch%20Wilmore%2C%20will%2C%20Mr%20Tyson%20said%2C%20explaining%20he%20was%20never%20worried%20about%20their%20safety%20or%20about%20them%20returning%20home.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20professional%20astronauts...%20they%20are%20selected%20not%20just%20because%20they%20are%20physically%20fit%20but%20also%20because%20they%20are%20emotionally%20fit%2C%20okay%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20you%20are%20emotionally%20fit%2C%20things%20like%2C%20'okay%2C%20instead%20of%20eight%20days%20it's%20nine%20months'...%20you%20don't%20see%20them%20freaking%20out%20or%20reacting%20in%20some%20way%20that%20would%20jeopardise%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20crew.%20So%20that's%20why%20I%20was%20never%20worried...%20even%20if%20everybody%20else%20was.%20At%20no%20time%20did%20I%20have%20sympathy%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20they%20needed%20sympathy%2C%20personally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20Mr%20Wilmore's%20road%20to%20recovery%2C%20Neil%20deGrasse%20Tyson%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20think%20their%20muscles%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20hold%20them%20up...%20on%20the%20ISS%20they%20have%20many%20ways%20to%20exercise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20difference%20is...%20when%20you%20spend%20this%20much%20time%20being%20weightless%2C%20your%20ability%20to%20orient%20for%20what%20is%20'up'%20and%20'down'%20is%20compromised%20because%20you%20never%20had%20to%20use%20these%20tools%20of%20the%20inner%20ear%20to%20establish%20'up'%20and%20'down'%20in%20space.%20Now%20I%20haven't%20been%20in%20space...%20but%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20astronauts%2C%20friends%20of%20mine%2C%20who%20have%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20there%2C%20and%20they%20say%20typically%20they%20will%20recover%20within%20a%20week...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20don't%20hand%20them%20glass%20cutlery%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20if%20you%20hand%20them%20a%20glass%20they%20just%20let%20go%20(because%20their%20muscles%20are%20weaker)%20So%2C%20make%20sure%20the%20first%20few%20beverages%20are%20in%20a%20plastic%20cup%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tyson%20said%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tyson%20also%20played%20down%20any%20talk%20of%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20Mr%20Wilmore's%20mental%20status%20being%20affected%2C%20pointing%20out%20NASA%20selects%20its%20astronauts%20based%20on%20both%20strength%20of%20body%20and%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunita%20Williams%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Sunita%20Williams%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fseb0m1f_sunita-williams_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Williams%20onboard%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(File).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20food%20and%20water%20(even%20if%20it%20was%20recycled%20urine%2C%20which%20is%20normal%20up%20there!)%20and%20they%20are%20professional%20astronauts.%20The%20only%20thing...%20maybe%20they%20didn't%20bring%20extra%20pairs%20of%20underwear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%2C%20and%20fellow%20astronaut%20Butch%20Wilmore%2C%20were%20flown%20back%20from%20the%20ISS%20late%20Tuesday%2Fearly%20Wednesday.%20They%20returned%20home%20in%20SpaceX's%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20and%20were%20greeted%20by%20a%20pod%20of%20chattering%20dolphins%20as%20they%20splashed%20down%20of%20Florida's%20eastern%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwatch-dolphins-welcome-sunita-williams-butch-wilmore-back-home-7955654%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20Saying%20'Hi'%26quot%3B%3A%20Dolphins%20Welcome%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20Home%20From%20Space%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20flown%20to%20the%20ISS%20on%20June%205%20last%20year.%20But%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20capsule%20that%20carried%20them%20to%20the%20ISS%20then%20had%20propulsion%20issues%2C%20meaning%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20Mr%20Wilmore%20had%20to%20wait...%20for%20nine%20months%2C%20during%20which%20time%20the%20United%20States%20held%20a%20presidential%20election%2C%20to%20come%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVIDEO%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwatch-the-moment-sunita-williams-butch-wilmore-dragon-spacecraft-splashed-down-off-florida-coast-7955622%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoment%20Sunita%20Williams'%20Spacecraft%20Splashed%20Down%20Off%20Florida%20Coast%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20they%20are%2C%20and%20visuals%20of%20the%20astronauts%20(and%20the%20two%20sent%20to%20bring%20them%20back)%20waving%20and%20smiling%20from%20inside%20the%20capsule%20after%20it%20landed%20on%20Earth%20were%20beamed%20live%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20back%20home%2C%20though%2C%20is%20only%20half%20the%20challenge%20to%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20returning%20to%20normal%20lives.%20The%20other%20involves%20a%20months-long%20rehabilitation%20programme%20to%20rebuild%20muscle%20mass%20and%20bone%20density%3B%20this%20will%20include%20strength%20training%20and%20mobility%20exercises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frn3tkt3o_sunita-williams_625x300_19_March_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20thumbs-up%20from%20a%20smiling%20Sunita%20Williams%20as%20she%20returns%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3