E%3Cp%3ENatural%20language%20expert%20Satya%20Nitta%2C%20CEO%20of%20Emergence%20AI%2C%20a%20company%20specializing%20in%20multi-agent%20systems%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20agents%20are%20designed%20to%20troubleshoot%20even%20as%20their%20surroundings%20constantly%20evolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20go%20%26quot%3Bbeyond%20automation%2C%20demonstrating%20contextual%20reasoning%2C%20adapting%20to%20unforeseen%20challenges%2C%20and%20dynamically%20adjusting%20plans%20to%20succeed%20in%20complex%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20Nitta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20to%20think%20about%20agents%20is%20in%20relation%20to%20large%20language%20models%2C%20which%20serve%20as%20the%20basis%20for%20popular%20chatbots%20like%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20large%20language%20model%20is%20a%20misnomer.%20It%20should%20really%20be%20called%20a%20neural%20sequence%20model%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20any%20sequential%20data%3A%20natural%20language%2C%20programming%20languages%2C%20pixel%20sequences%2C%20and%20biological%20sequences%20(proteins)%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-search-monopoly-you-com-ceo-richard-socher-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERichard%20Socher%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20You.com%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20search%20engine%20for%20knowledge%20workers%2C%20told%20BI.%20An%20agent%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20neural%20sequence%20model%20that%20can%20take%20actions%20for%20you%2C%20learning%20from%20patterns%20of%20human%20behavior%20to%20automate%20complex%20tasks%20across%20multiple%20domains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20agents%20become%20more%20ingrained%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20people%20may%20start%20to%20think%20of%20them%20as%20team%20members%20or%20authoritative%20assistants.%20But%20Spence%20Green%2C%20CEO%20of%20AI-powered%20translation%20company%20LILT%2C%20who%20has%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20natural%20language%20processing%2C%20said%2C%2