20a%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20owners%2C%20especially%20self-employed%20individuals%2C%20often%20benefit%20from%20filing%20a%20tax%20extension%2C%20Schultz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20so%20gives%20small-business%20owners%20more%20flexibility%20in%20making%20their%20retirement%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20business%20retirement%20plans%20%26quot%3Bare%20based%20on%20how%20much%20taxable%20income%20the%20business%20shows%2C%26quot%3B%20Schultz%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20IRS%20needs%20to%20give%20you%20enough%20time%20to%20finalize%20what%20your%20business%20income%20is%20going%20to%20look%20like%20on%20its%20tax%20return%20in%20order%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20you're%20eligible%20for%20these%20plans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tax%20extension%20gives%20you%20more%20time%20to%20save%20and%20contribute%20to%20a%20plan%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20cash%20readily%20available%20in%20April%2C%20but%20still%20treat%20it%20as%20a%202024%20deduction.%20Or%2C%20if%20you%20haven't%20set%20up%20a%20retirement%20plan%20yet%2C%20a%20tax%20extension%20gives%20you%20more%20time%20to%20create%20one%20and%20still%20contribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20strategy%20is%20most%20common%20with%20IRA%20and%20SEP%20IRA%20plans%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20be%20a%20great%20fit%20for%20those%20with%20profit-sharing%20and%20pension-style%20retirement%20plans%2C%20according%20to%20Schultz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286638182-38d7-4a8a-bdea-798b840c31d0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDonations%20to%20charity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Ftax-deductible-donations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonations%20to%20charity%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20tax-deductible%2C%20but%20only%20if%20you%20follow%20the%20correct%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20make%20a%20donation%20of%20over%20%245%2C000%2C%20the%20IRS%20will%20request%20an%20appraisal%20to%20back%20up%20your%20deduction%2C%20Schultz%20said.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20proper%20documentation%2C%20the%20IRS%20might%20deny%20your%20tax%20deduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20a%20client%20might%20have%20made%20a%20donation%20to%20a%20charity%20and%20they%20haven't%20gotten%20the%20final%20appraisal%20back%20from%20the%20appraiser%20by%20April%2015th%2C%26quot%3B%20Schultz%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20a%20very%20common%20example%20where%20we%20would%20recommend%20taxpayers%20to%20file%20an%20extension%20and%20give%20themselves%20more%20time%20to%20get%20that%20information%20to%20support%20their%20charitable%20deduction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d9f7a29-fc89-422c-bbc0-fe7184e6461a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlternative%20investments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENon-traditional%20investments%20outside%20of%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20can%20pose%20tax%20challenges%2C%20which%20is%20why%20extending%20your%20filing%20deadline%20might%20be%20a%20safe%20bet%20to%20ensure%20your%20documents%20are%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20who%20are%20limited%20partners%20in%20a%20private%20equity%20fund%20won't%20receive%20tax%20documents%20by%20the%20traditional%20April%20filing%20date%20due%20to%20the%20more%20complicated%20nature%20of%20the%20investment.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20would%20need%20to%20file%20an%20extension%20to%20accurately%20complete%20their%20tax%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IRS%20does%20not%20require%20private%20equity%20funds%20or%20hedge%20funds%20or%20limited%20partnerships%20to%20provide%20tax%20information%20until%20September%2015th%20of%20the%20year%20after%2C%26quot%3B%20Schultz%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20I'm%20invested%20and%20I'm%20a%20limited%20partner%20in%20an%20investment%20fund%20of%20some%20sort%2C%20I%20might%20not%20get%20my%202024%20tax%20reporting%20on%20the%20activity%20from%20that%20fund%20until%20early%20September%202025.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20complex%20private%20investments%2C%20either.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-oleary-crypto-out-of-cowboy-era-under-trump-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecryptocurrency%3C%2Fa%3E%20platforms%20might%20not%20send%20you%20a%201099%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20report%20your%20activity.%20An%20extension%20can%20be%20useful%20if%20you%20need%20extra%20time%20to%20organize%20your%20crypto%20paperwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffile-taxes-extension-october-deadline-paperwork-retirement-plans-small-business-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742459402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db1aadb8b41a9673fb222a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffile-taxes-extension-october-deadline-paperwork-retirement-plans-small-business-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taxpayers%20have%20the%20option%20to%20request%20a%20tax%20extension%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20six%20additional%20months%20to%20file%20your%20taxes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cji%40businessinsider.com%20(Christine%20Ji)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffile-taxes-extension-october-deadline-paperwork-retirement-plans-small-business-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CEO%20shares%20secret%20to%20creating%20this%20unique%20aircraft%20the%20Navy%20is%20investing%20over%20%247%20million%20in%20to%20fly%20parts%20to%20broken%20warships%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222639%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22PteroDynamics%20Transwing%20design%2C%20the%20XP-4%2C%20in%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d6da7769253ccddf996514%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221485%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPteroDynamics%20makes%20the%20Transwing%2C%20as%20seen%20here%20in%20the%20X-P4%20model.%20The%20wings%20can%20fold%20around%20the%20fuselage%2C%20remain%20halfway%20open%2C%20or%20move%20to%20full%20fixed-wing%20flight.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20PteroDynamics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20is%20looking%20into%20using%20drones%20to%20deliver%20critical%20repair%20cargo%20to%20broken%20warships.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20BlueWater%20Maritime%20Logistics%20UAS%20project%20seeks%20innovative%20VTOL%20designs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20unique%20PteroDynamics%20Transwing%20design%20recently%20received%20a%20%244.65%20million%20contract%20expansion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20wants%20to%20know%20if%20roughly%20motorcycle-sized%20drones%20can%20do%20what%20its%20larger%20piloted%20workhorse%20helicopter%20and%20tiltrotor%20aircraft%20are%20currently%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20flying%20critical%20repair%20cargo%20out%20to%20broken%20warships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritical%20repair%20parts%20for%20incapacitated%20warships%2C%20such%20as%20circuit%20boards%2C%20o-rings%2C%20or%20pumps%2C%20around%20half%20the%20time%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eweigh%20less%20than%20a%20pound.%20The%20current%20delivery%20approach%20wastes%20fuel%20and%20other%20resources%20and%20puts%20a%20lot%20of%20unnecessary%20wear%20and%20tear%20on%20Military%20Sealift%20Command's%20H-60%20and%20V-22%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20really%20needs%20a%20heavy%2C%20crewed%20aircraft%20for%20this.%20There%20just%20isn't%20a%20proven%20alternative%2C%20at%20least%20not%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolving%20that%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20the%20primary%20focus%20of%20the%20Navy's%20BlueWater%20Maritime%20Logistics%20UAS%20project%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20major%20opportunity%20for%20defense%20tech%20firms%20like%20Colorado-based%20PteroDynamics%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20is%20valuable.%20It%20needs%20to%20get%20somewhere%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20get%20to.%20It%20has%20to%20get%20there%20quickly.%20It's%20time-sensitive.%20And%20people%20are%20paying%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20today%20to%20do%20that%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20PteroDynamics%20CEO%20Matthew%20Graczyk%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22PteroDynamics%20Transwing%20design%2C%20the%20XP-4%2C%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20a%20warship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d6dac969253ccddf996517%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPteroDynamics%20worked%20with%20the%20Navy%20to%20test%20the%20Transwing%20design%20during%20the%20Rim%20of%20the%20Pacific%20naval%20exercise%20last%20year.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20PteroDynamics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20recently%20picked%20up%20a%20%244.65%20million%20contract%20expansion%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%3ENaval%20Air%20Warfare%20Center%20Aircraft%20Division%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20the%20development%20of%20its%20novel%20Transwing%20aircraft%20design%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20contract%20value%20to%20over%20%247%20million.%20The%20new%20funding%20will%20support%20development%20of%20a%20new%20Transwing%20model%2C%20the%20XP-5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20companies%20have%20contributed%20BlueWater%20UAS%20ideas%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20variations%20of%20classic%20designs.%20The%20Transwing%2C%20as%20an%20articulating-%20or%20%26quot%3Bcracking-wing%26quot%3B%20design%2C%20is%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20interesting%20design%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BlueWater%20project%20lead%2C%20Bill%20Macchione%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20aim%20as%20the%20Navy%20evaluates%20uncrewed%20vertical%20takeoff%20and%20landing%20(VTOL)%20designs%20is%20to%20find%20innovations%20with%20reduced%20complexity%20both%20in%20the%20engineering%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20what%20was%20very%20interesting%20about%20the%20PteroDynamics%20design%20being%20an%20articulating%20wing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It's%20a%20%26quot%3Bsimple%20linear%20actuator%20that%20basically%20just%20articulates%20the%20wings%20on%20a%20pivot%2C%20and%20those%20pushers%2C%20those%20traditional%20propellers%20in%20fixed%20wing%2C%20become%20the%20lift%20propellers%20in%20VTOL%20mode.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ea9b005-cefc-4ecd-96a7-bbc66a0db700%5C%22%3E'That's%20where%20disruption%20happens'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20VTOL%20aircraft%20designs%20were%20early%20helicopters.%20Then%20came%20designs%20like%20lift%20jets%2C%20tail-sitter%20aircraft%2C%20and%20tilt%20rotors.%20PteroDynamics%20has%20now%20patented%20a%20new%20design%20that%20leverages%20the%20propellers%20in%20all%20flight%20modes%20and%20can%20fold%20the%20wings%20around%20the%20fuselage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20wings%20stretch%20out%20in%20the%20cruise%20phase%20of%20flight%20and%20fold%20back%20during%20vertical%20flight%20to%20a%20configuration%20resembling%20a%20quadcopter%20during%20take-off%20and%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraczyk%20calls%20the%20Transwing%20design%20%26quot%3BVTOL%203.0.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22PteroDynamics%20Transwing%20design%2C%20the%20XP-4%2C%20in%20VTOL%20mode.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d6db8369253ccddf99651d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Transwing%20is%20unusual%20because%20it%20breaks%20away%20from%20traditional%20VTOL%20aircraft%20designs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20PteroDynamics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20design%20came%20from%20Val%20Petrov%2C%20a%20mathematician%2C%20chemist%2C%20and%20expert%20in%20nonlinear%20dynamics%20who%20spent%20years%20in%20asset%20and%20capital%20management.%20He%20wasn't%20an%20aviation%20engineer%2C%20but%20he%20was%2C%20as%20Graczyk%20told%20BI%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Btinkerer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20ask%20someone%20who%20is%20educated%20in%20a%20field%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20a%20field%2C%20how%20to%20solve%20a%20problem%2C%20they%20go%20into%20how%20they've%20been%20taught%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20Graczyk%20said%2C%20and%20you%20ultimately%20end%20up%20with%20a%20variation%20of%20an%20existing%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20ask%20a%20guy%20who%20has%20not%20been%20taught%20how%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%20that's%20where%20innovation%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20telling%20BI%20that%20is%20the%20key%20to%20making%20something%20new.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20disruption%20happens.%20That%20is%20how%20Petrov%20was%20able%20to%20conceive%20of%20this%20Transwing%20that%20didn't%20come%20from%20Airbus%20or%20Lockheed%20or%20Raytheon%20or%20Boeing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPetrov%20is%20PteroDynamics'%20founder%20and%20chairman%20of%20its%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20PteroDynamics%20design%20is%20what%20the%20Navy%20ultimately%20needs%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20but%20the%20service%20is%20interested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20other%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20designs%20being%20looked%20at%20and%20tested%20by%20the%20Navy%20as%20part%20of%20the%20BlueWater%20program%20include%20Skyways%20V2.6%2C%20ShieldAI's%20V-BAT%2C%20and%20Sierra%20Nevada%20Corporation's%20Voly-50%2C%20among%20others%20featuring%20their%20own%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227cb2a4eb-f8e3-4bab-9ea1-2bfb3dd9da60%5C%22%3E'The%20world%20is%20changing'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy's%20BlueWater%20UAS%20technology%20development%20program%20started%20years%20ago%2C%20evolving%20from%20a%202018%20study%20that%20found%20about%2048%25%20of%20all%20critical%20repair%20cargo%20being%20flown%20out%20to%20ships%20by%20Military%20Sealift%20Command%20aircraft%20is%20under%2016%20ounces%2C%20smaller%20than%20a%20regular%20water%20bottle.%20The%20study%20found%20that%2076%25%20of%20all%20parts%20are%20under%2010%20pounds%2C%20and%2090%25%20are%20under%2050%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20is%20interested%20in%20determining%20whether%20VTOL%20drones%20weighing%20under%20330%20pounds%20can%20run%20these%20delivery%20missions%20instead%20of%20crewed%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drones%20have%20to%20be%20able%20to%20fly%20400%20nautical%20miles%20round%20trip%2C%20perhaps%20eventually%201%2C000%20miles%2C%20on%20a%20mixture%20of%20electricity%20and%20JP-5%20fuel%20with%20a%2050-pound%20payload%20stored%20internally%20and%20land%20on%20the%20deck%20of%20a%20moving%20ship%20at%20sea%20without%20any%20support%20infrastructure%20and%20minimal%20sailor%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20small%20drones%20points%20to%20big%20cost%20savings.%20Each%20Sikorsky%20SH-60%2FMH-60%20Seahawk%20costs%20over%20%2430%20million%20and%20requires%20two%20fully%20trained%20and%20proficient%20human%20pilots.%20That%20is%20not%20even%20factoring%20in%20the%20operational%20and%20sustainment%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20drones%2C%20there%20also%20has%20to%20be%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22PteroDynamics%20Transwing%20design%2C%20the%20XP-4%2C%20in%20flight.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d6dbe1585f1dff88b249cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPteroDynamics%20expects%20that%20the%20Transwing%20design%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%2030-year%20aircraft%20design%2C%20one%20that%20will%20persist%20through%20evolutions%20in%20this%20technology%20space.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20PteroDynamics%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20where%20somebody%20is%20sitting%20with%20a%20controller%20in%20their%20hand%20and%20controlling%20the%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20Graczyk%20said%20of%20the%20Transwing.%20%26quot%3BYou%20lay%20out%20your%20mission%20on%20a%20computer%2C%20so%20just%20one%20laptop%2C%20an%20operator%2C%20and%20an%20aircraft%2C%20that's%20all%20you%20need%2C%20and%20you%20communicate%20the%20mission%20to%20the%20aircraft.%20You%20push%20go%2C%20and%20it%20takes%20off%2C%20does%20the%20mission%2C%20and%20lands.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20involved%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20a%20certain%20extent%2C%20it%20can%20make%20decisions%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20a%20drone%20to%20fly%20that%20mission%20is%20nothing%20like%20Amazon%20drone%20deliveries.%20Amazon%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20adversaries%20trying%20to%20shoot%20them%20down%20or%20jam%20their%20communications.%20And%20there%20is%20also%20no%20need%20to%20land%20it%20on%20a%20moving%20target%20in%20an%20unforgiving%20delivery%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLanding%20on%20ships%20and%20working%20around%20ships%20is%20not%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Bruening%2C%20the%20director%20of%20MSC's%20Taluga%20Group%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeeting%20the%20tough%20operational%20expectations%20of%20the%20Navy's%20BlueWater%20technology%20development%20program%20is%20a%20complex%20technological%20challenge%20that%20the%20Navy%20has%20been%20working%20with%20a%20range%20of%20companies%20to%20overcome.%20The%20project%20is%20not%20yet%20a%20program%20of%20record%20and%20is%20experimental%20for%20now.%20Still%2C%20this%20is%20clearly%20where%20military%20technology%20is%20heading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20Graczyk%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20geopolitics%20changing%2C%20we're%20seeing%20the%20way%20warfare%20is%20conducted%20changing%2C%20and%20the%20way%20diplomacy%20is%20conducted%2C%20all%20of%20that's%20changing.%20There%20is%20a%20particular%20shift%20in%20bias%20toward%20higher%20volume%2C%20lower%20cost%20autonomous%20systems%20that%20are%20attritable%2C%20that%20are%20expendable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20tremendous%20possibilities%20and%20%26quot%3Ban%20evolutionary%20introduction%20into%20the%20market%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20key%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20use%20this%20revolutionary%20technology%20to%20solve%20problems%20that%20exist%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpterodynamics-ceo-shares-secret-to-transwing-vtol-aircraft-innovation-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742459222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d6dc48b8b41a9673facb9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpterodynamics-ceo-shares-secret-to-transwing-vtol-aircraft-innovation-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unusual%20Transwing%20aircraft%20design%20has%20the%20Navy's%20interest.%20The%20PteroDynamics%20CEO%20told%20BI%20the%20trick%20to%20creating%20it%20came%20from%20outside%20the%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rpickrell%40businessinsider.com%20(Ryan%20Pickrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpterodynamics-ceo-shares-secret-to-transwing-vtol-aircraft-innovation-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20visa%20checks%20don't%20end%20at%20approval%3A%20What%20Indian%20travellers%20must%20know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742458997000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fus-visa-checks-don-t-end-at-approval-what-indian-travellers-must-know-125032000488_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Visa%20holders%20are%20continuously%20monitored%20to%20ensure%20they%20comply%20with%20all%20US%20laws%20and%20immigration%20rules%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%