20around%20that%20petition%2C%20leaving%20aside%20the%20Aurangzeb%20issue.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20name%20the%20people%20who%20are%20behind%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Raut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%20efforts%20to%20defame%20the%20Thackeray%20family%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20the%20culture%20of%20Maharashtra%20to%20throw%20mud%20on%20the%20future%20and%20career%20of%20a%20young%20leader%20in%20this%20way.%20These%20experiments%20were%20done%20on%20many%20leaders%20like%20us.%20Nothing%20came%20out%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raut%20warned%20of%20politics%20around%20the%20issue.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20many%20such%20cases%20happen%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20families%20seek%20justice%20but%20five%20years%20later%2C%20they%20come%20out%20and%20say%2C%20they%20were%20pressurised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Ambadas%20Danve%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Bconspiring%20to%20defame%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray.%20Speaking%20to%20media%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20matter%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20court.%20We%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20he%20(Disha's%20father)%20has%20said%2C%20but%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20is%20a%20mature%20leader%2C%20a%20young%20leader.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20conspiring%20to%20defame%20him%20by%20putting%20pressure%20on%20him.%20We%20don't%20need%20to%20answer%20to%20this%20conspiracy.%20The%20court%20will%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra's%20former%20Home%20Minister%20and%20NCP%20(SP)%20leader%20Anil%20Deshmukh%20also%20called%20it%20a%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20taking%20information%20on%20the%20plea%20filed%20by%20Disha%20Salina's%20father.%20All%20this%20now%20looks%20like%20a%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20side%2C%20late%20Bollyw