ngs%20that%20we%20would%20get%20by%20moving%20to%20Portland%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wound%20up%20getting%20more%20for%20a%20lot%2C%20lot%20less%2C%20which%20allowed%20us%20to%20invest%20back%20into%20the%20stock%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeremy%20Smith%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Mary%20Jo%2C%20in%20their%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d42e76585f1dff88b227b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeremy%20Smith%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Mary%20Jo%2C%20sold%20their%20primary%20home%20in%20San%20Ramon%2C%20California%2C%20for%20%241.5%20million%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20market%20in%202021.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jeremy%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e043a3e-b766-46da-9850-9ecc3c9a70a2%5C%22%3EA%20community%20of%20Californians%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20loving%20the%20Portland%20area%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20Smith%20misses%20California.%20He%20yearns%20for%20warmer%20weather%2C%20sunshine%2C%20ocean%20views%2C%20and%20living%20closer%20to%20his%20three%20children%20and%20grandchildren.%20He%20says%20he%20visits%20about%20four%20times%20a%20year%20to%20see%20his%20kids%20and%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20miss%20the%20hell%20out%20of%20California%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it's%20expensive%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20magical%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20loves%20being%20surrounded%20by%20Oregon's%20many%20rivers%20and%20Lake%20Oswego%2C%20where%20his%20wife%20kayaks%20regularly%20with%20her%20friends.%20And%20the%20food%20is%20excellent%20in%20Portland%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Smith%20may%20have%20left%20California%2C%20he's%20still%20surrounded%20by%20Californians.%20He%20estimates%20that%2012%20of%20the%2014%20homes%20in%20his%20gated%20neighborhood%20are%20owned%20by%20people%20who%20move