20roles%20at%20former%20employers%2C%20only%20to%20be%20mysteriously%20ghosted%20by%20recruiters%20or%20quietly%20marked%20as%20%26quot%3Bineligible%20for%20rehire.%26quot%3B%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20affected%20individuals%20claimed%20they%20had%20strong%20performance%20records%20and%20no%20history%20of%20workplace%20misconduct.%20All%20of%20them%20requested%20for%20their%20identities%20and%20the%20names%20of%20their%20workplaces%20to%20be%20kept%20anonymous%20to%20prevent%20retaliation%20from%20their%20former%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a544772-d33a-4e29-a16d-d1ae20ba20e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BA%20special%20kind%20of%20cruelty%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20employee%20from%20the%20consulting%20industry%20who%20described%20their%20experience%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI%20said%20that%20they%20found%20themselves%20on%20a%20block%20list%20after%20they%20quit%20because%20of%20workplace%20politics.%20This%20employee%20said%20that%20they%20found%20out%20they%20were%20on%20a%20list%20from%20the%20company's%20HR%20department%20after%20applying%20to%20multiple%20roles%20since%20they%20left.%20%26quot%3BTo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20%5BI%5D%20confirmed%20that%20it's%20still%20happening%20even%20after%20eight%20years%20of%20leaving%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20were%20exploring%20legal%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20employee%20of%20a%20major%20chip%20company%20who%20was%20part%20of%20a%20wave%20of%20layoffs%20in%202015%20said%20they%20were%20told%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bbanned%20for%20life%26quot%3B%20from%20working%20at%20the%20company%20despite%20a%20promotion%20and%20a%20raise%20right%20before%20the%20cut.%20%26quot%3BWhy%3F%20No%20one%20seems%20to%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20it%20seems%20likely%20that%20I%20will%20never%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20employee%20of%20the%20same%20chip%20company%20told%20BI%20that%20their%20manager%20put%20them%20on%20a%20list%20after%20they%20left%20due%20to%20disagreements.%20When%20managers%2C%20including%20ones%20this%20person%20had%20known%20for%20years%2C%20tried%20to%20rehire%20them%20over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to.%20%26quot%3BAt%20one%20point%2C%20I%20checked%20with%20HR%2C%20and%20they%20confirmed%20to%20me%20that%20I%20was%20on%20a%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20told%20me%20that%20a%20manager%20could%20overturn%20the%20decision%2C%20but%20that%20never%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20companies%2C%20human%20resources%20have%20designated%20alternate%20names%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bblock%26quot%3B%20list.%20An%20engineer%20who%20worked%20for%20a%20large%20publicly%20traded%20internet%20company%20based%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20from%202010%20to%202014%20told%20BI%20that%20these%20block%20lists%20existed%20at%20the%20company%2C%20too%2C%20but%20with%20a%20different%20categorization.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20strong%20performance%20reviews%20for%20multiple%20consecutive%20performance%20cycles%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20resigned%2C%20I%20was%20put%20on%20a%20'non-regretted%20attrition'%20list.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20former%20manager%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20same%20company%20from%202009%20through%202016%20in%20multiple%20countries%20said%20that%20a%20label%20called%20%26quot%3Bnon-regretted%20attrition%26quot%3B%20when%20an%20employee%20quit%20would%20essentially%20block%20them%20from%20being%20rehired.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20people%20deciding%20which%20category%20someone%20who%20left%20fell%20into%20was%20HR%20and%20the%20direct%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20if%20you%20were%20'regretted%20attrition%2C'%20you%20would%20be%20fast-tracked%20for%20interviews%20and%20at%20least%20guaranteed%20a%20recruiter%20screen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20emails%20and%20messages%20to%20Business%20Insider%20came%20from%20frustrated%20ex-workers%20from%20Meta.%20Three%20former%20Meta%20employees%20who%20were%20laid%20off%20along%20with%20thousands%20of%20other%20workers%20in%202022%20told%20BI%20that%20multiple%20hiring%20managers%20who%20had%20tried%20to%20rehire%20them%20were%20told%20by%20HR%20that%20these%20former%20employees%20were%20on%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20hire%26quot%3B%20lists%20and%20could%20not%20be%20hired%20back.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20those%20opportunities%20ended%20in%20mysterious%20dead%20ends%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20them%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20a%20special%20kind%20of%20cruelty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20said%20previous%20managers%20at%20the%20company%20ran%20%26quot%3Binto%20roadblocks%26quot%3B%20after%20having%20recruiters%20reach%20out%20to%20rehire%20them.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20conversation%20with%20someone%20from%20HR%2C%20I%20was%20told%20there%20is%20a%20'do%20not%20engage'%20flag%20against%20my%20name%20in%20their%20system%20despite%20having%20good%20performance%20ratings%20during%20my%20time%20at%20Meta%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Meta%20spokesperson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-secret-block-lists-bar-rehiring-some-former-employees-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20had%20%26quot%3Bclear%20criteria%20for%20when%20someone%20is%20marked%20ineligible%20for%20rehire%20that%20are%20applied%20to%20all%20departing%20employees%2C%20and%20there%20are%20checks%20and%20balances%20in%20the%20process%20so%20that%20a%20single%20manager%20cannot%20unilaterally%20tag%20someone%20ineligible%20without%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20said%20that%20its%20decision%20to%20bar%20an%20ex-employee%20from%20rehire%20is%20based%20on%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20determine%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20separation%2C%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20employee's%20departure%20%E2%80%94%20policy%20violation%2C%20performance%20termination%2C%20voluntary%20resignation%20etc.%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%2C%20along%20with%20the%20last%20rating%20prior%20to%20separation%20and%20any%20other%20recent%20performance%20signals%2C%20determines%20whether%20an%20employee%20is%20eligible%20for%20rehire%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7a08445-2da0-4326-a11f-54cf2df740c2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlock%20lists%20across%20all%20industries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20nurse%20with%2038%20years%20of%20experience%20claimed%20that%20even%20hospitals%20around%20the%20country%20keep%20block%20lists%20after%20unsuccessfully%20trying%20to%20get%20rehired%20at%20previous%20workplaces%20and%20hearing%20from%20HR%20that%20they%20weren't%20eligible%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20manager%20has%20a%20beef%20against%20an%20employee%2C%20they%20can%20easily%20keep%20them%20from%20being%20hired%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20punitive%2C%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20you%20can%20do%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Reddit%2C%20dozens%20of%20people%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Ftechnology%2Fcomments%2F1j4kyia%2Fmeta_keeps_block_lists_of_exemployees_and_even%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20talked%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20commonplace%20the%20practice%20seems%20to%20be.%20One%20user%20shared%20how%20their%20company's%20internal%20block%20list%20functioned%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20leave%20for%20a%20competitor%2C%20you're%20automatically%20flagged%20as%20'do%20not%20rehire.'%20There's%20no%20discussion%2C%20no%20appeal%20%E2%80%94%20just%20an%20invisible%20wall%20you%20don't%20even%20know%20exists%20until%20you%20try%20coming%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20do%20input%20whether%20you%20are%20eligible%20for%20rehire%20in%20their%20human%20capital%20management%20(HCM)%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20career%20coach%20Marlo%20Lyons%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20put%20'not%20eligible%20for%20rehire%2C'%20which%20many%20fired%20employees%20are%2C%20then%20you%20would%20not%20be%20rehired%20no%20matter%20how%20you've%20changed%20or%20grown%20and%20no%20matter%20if%20you%20applied%20to%20a%20different%20department.%20%5BIt%5D%20does%20raise%20questions%20about%20how%20these%20decisions%20are%20made%20and%20whether%20employees%20have%20any%20recourse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e64e2684-9aca-412c-a792-a1548b5aa6d6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%2C%20systematic%20approach%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20LinkedIn%2C%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20people%20weighed%20in%20on%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-former-hr-chief-astonished-meta-internal-block-lists-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Laszlo%20Bock%2C%20a%20former%20Google%20HR%20head%2C%20who%20was%20surprised%20by%20Meta's%20block%20lists%20that%20BI%20reported%20about.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20heard%20of%20anything%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Bock%20wrote%20on%20the%20platform.%20%26quot%3BI've%20sometimes%20heard%20an%20exec%20say%2C%20'Don't%20ever%20re-hire%20this%20person%2C'%20but%20never%20seen%20a%20large-scale%2C%20systematic%20approach%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaren%20Liska%2C%20an%20attorney%20and%20Director%20of%20People%20Operations%20at%20SafeSend%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20comment%20on%20Bock's%20post%20that%20some%20companies%20used%20such%20lists%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20risk%20mitigation%20strategy%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%20there%20could%20be%20issues%20with%20their%20implementation.%20%26quot%3BLike%20any%20other%20tool%20in%20a%20large%20org%20that%20is%20meant%20to%20help%20keep%20systems%20functioning%2C%20it%20can%20be%20used%20for%20protective%20purposes%20or%20other%20legitimate%20business%20reasons%2C%20or%20it%20can%20be%20used%20improperly%20as%20part%20of%20retaliation%20or%20to%20maintain%20discriminatory%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20Liska%20wrote.%20She%20questioned%20whether%20these%20lists%20should%20have%20expiration%20dates%20%26quot%3Bto%20give%20people%20a%20chance%20to%20learn%20and%20grow%20or%20for%20the%20security%2Frevenge%20risk%20to%20cool%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERehiring%20former%20employees%20can%20be%20a%20business%20risk%2C%20Liska%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%20They%20might%20need%20performance%20interventions%2C%20or%20resume%20past%20negative%20behaviours%20like%20poor%20attendance.%20%26quot%3BAn%20'ineligible%20for%20rehire'%20list%20helps%20protect%20against%20these%20risks%20by%20ensuring%20that%20regardless%20of%20turnover%20in%20HR%20or%20leadership%2C%20there%20is%20a%20source%20of%20knowledge%20within%20the%20business%20about%20which%20former%20employees%20may%20not%20be%20viable%20future%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20is%20fired%20or%20laid%20off%2C%20being%20ineligible%20for%20rehire%20should%20be%20communicated%2C%20Liska%20said.%20And%20companies%20should%20have%20a%20policy%20for%20re-evaluating%20the%20reasons%20someone%20is%20placed%20on%20a%20list%20to%20begin%20with%20to%20leave%20a%20potential%20opening%20in%20the%20future%20when%20there%20isn't%20a%20significant%20legal%20risk.%20%26quot%3BPerhaps%20a%20different%20manager%2C%20or%20a%20different%20line%20of%20work%2C%20or%20just%20gaining%20more%20experience%20could%20make%20all%20the%20difference%20and%20turn%20an%20underperforming%20or%20unhappy%20former%20employee%20into%20a%20productive%20and%20happy%20returning%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiska%20believes%20it's%20time%20to%20have%20an%20industry-wide%20conversation%20about%20this%20practice.%20%26quot%3BSimply%20saying%20'don't%20have%20these%20lists%20at%20all'%20without%20a%20viable%20alternative%20ignores%20the%20difficulties%20of%20managing%20large%20companies%20at%20scale.%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20employees%2C%20the%20existence%20of%20block%20lists%20introduces%20yet%20another%20layer%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20an%20already%20ruthless%20job%20market.%20While%20companies%20argue%20that%20blocking%20certain%20employees%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20business%20strategy%20or%20risk%20management%2C%20critics%20say%20the%20practice%20disproportionately%20harms%20workers%20who%20may%20have%20left%20on%20neutral%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20hyper-competitive%20job%20market%2C%20the%20question%20isn't%20just%20whether%20you'll%20be%20welcomed%20back%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20whether%20the%20door%20was%20silently%20locked%20behind%20you%20the%20moment%20you%20walked%20out.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%20contributed%20reporting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you're%20a%20current%20or%20former%20Meta%20employee%20or%20have%20an%20insight%20to%20share%20about%20the%20company%2C%20contact%20Pranav%20Dixit%20from%20a%20nonwork%20device%20securely%20on%20Signal%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B1-408-905-9124%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%2B1-408-905-9124%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20email%20him%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Apranavdixit%40protonmail.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Epranavdixit%40protonmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-block-lists-affect-your-job-search-and-career-advancement-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742457602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67db308969253ccddf99c1e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-block-lists-affect-your-job-search-and-career-advancement-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Workers%20across%20industries%20repo