%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20hedge%20funds.%20For%20the%20average%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretail-investors-stock-market-bullish-sentiment-trump-trade-hood-pltr-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretail%20investor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20long-term%2C%20buy-and-hold%20strategy%20does%20just%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20simple%20enough.%20However%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Ritholtz%20Wealth%20Management%20finds%20that%20the%20biggest%20mistake%20investors%20make%20is%20not%20using%20this%20approach%20and%20instead%20letting%20emotions%20guide%20their%20decision-making%20and%20derail%20their%20long-term%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20rocket%20scientist%2C%20you%20just%20need%20to%20manage%20your%20own%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20earlier%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Nasdaq%20is%20down%204%25%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20what%20you%20experience%2C%20it's%20your%20reaction%20to%20those%20experiences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20as%20easy%20as%20it%20sounds%2C%20however.%20In%20his%20new%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20Not%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20Invest%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ERitholtz%20writes%20about%20Dr.%20William%20Bernstein%2C%20who%20unpacks%20the%20bodily%20forces%20that%20investors%20need%20to%20battle%2C%20like%20our%20limbic%20system%2C%20which%20manages%20our%20fight-or-flight%20responses%20and%20emotions.%20These%20are%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20animal%20spirits%20that%20market%20sages%20often%20say%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFail%20to%20manage%20your%20limbic%20system%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20you%20will%20die%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20Ritholtz%20said%20of%20Bernstein.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20incredible%20observation%20from%20somebody%20with%20a%20background%20in%20both%20neurology%20and%20investing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22626a2f79-a77e-4b76-9402-fda6115ee8e7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%20things%20investors%20should%20focus%20on%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20we%20overcome%20these%20hurdles%20to%20have%20our%20portfolios%20succeed%3F%20Instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20things%20out%20of%20their%20control%2C%20like%20macroeconomic%20trends%20or%20geopolitical%20developments%2C%20Ritholtz%20rattled%20off%20five%20variables%20that%20investors%20%3Cem%3Ecan%20%3C%2Fem%3Econtrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20is%20how%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20rate%20at%20which%20you%20are%20saving%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20You%20should%20be%20putting%20aside%20a%20fixed%20amount%20every%20month%20and%20sticking%20to%20it%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%20is%20%3Cstrong%3Ehow%20consistently%20you%20are%20buying%20into%20the%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20or%20dollar-cost%20averaging.%20The%20strategy%2C%20where%20you%20buy%20stocks%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%20(i.e.%20monthly)%2C%20allows%20investors%20to%20avoid%20trying%20to%20time%20the%20market%20by%20investing%20during%20both%20bull%20and%20bear%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%20is%20%3Cstrong%3Ewhether%20you%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20retirement%20vehicles%20like%20a%20401(k)%20or%20Roth%20IRA%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20They%20not%20only%20have%20various%20tax%20advantages%2C%20but%20employers%20often%20match%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20like%20free%20money%3F%20Then%20make%20sure%20to%20max%20out%20your%20401(k)%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20employer%20gives%20you%20a%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20Ritholtz%20writes%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourth%20is%20%3Cstrong%3Eportfolio%20structure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20or%20where%20exactly%20you%20have%20your%20money%20invested%20to%20set%20yourself%20up%20for%20your%20desired%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20much%20equity%20and%20bonds%20(e.g.%2070%2F30%2C%2060%2F40)%2C%20which%20fund%20do%20you%20want%20to%20own%20(VTI%2C%20SPY%2C%20VOO%2C%20ITOT%2C%20etc)%2C%20how%20globally%20diversified%20do%20you%20want%20to%20be%20(30%25%2C%2040%25%2C%2050%25)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%20is%20how%20well%20you%20%3Cstrong%3Eknow%20your%20risk%20profile%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Your%20investing%20timeline%20heavily%20influences%20this%3A%20if%20you%20need%20the%20money%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years'%20time%2C%20it's%20smarter%20to%20invest%20in%20lower-risk%20assets.%20If%20your%20timeline%20is%20multiple%20decades%2C%20riskier%20assets%20like%20stocks%20may%20be%20the%20way%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%2025%20years%20old%2C%20a%20market%20sell-off%20like%20this%20is%20a%20blessing%2C%26quot%3B%20Ritholtz%20said%20of%20the%20recent%20market%20volatility.%20%26quot%3BGo%20buy%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20and%20put%20it%20away%20for%2050%20years%2C%20and%20you'll%20be%20fine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%2050%20years%20old%20and%20you%20still%20have%2015-20%20years%20until%20retirement%2C%20well%20then%20I'm%20more%20inclined%20to%20say%20the%20total%20market%20is%20where%20you%20want%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-mistake-investors-make-investing-strategy-tips-barry-ritholtz-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742457602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d0ad32b8b41a9673fa5787%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-mistake-investors-make-investing-strategy-tips-barry-ritholtz-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20you're%2025%20years%20old%2C%20a%20market%20sell-off%20like%20this%20is%20a%20blessing%2C%26quot%3B%20Barry%20Ritholtz%20says%20of%20the%20recent%20market%20volatility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-mistake-investors-make-investing-strategy-