C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20shared%20their%20struggles%20with%20feeling%20unwelcome%20in%20Bengaluru%20due%20to%20regional%20biases.%20%26quot%3BRacist%20remarks%20made%20it%20very%20tough%20for%20me%20to%20feel%20accepted%20within%20my%20own%20country.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20constant%20reminder%20of%20how%20I'm%20from%20the%20'inferior'%20cow%20belt%20part%20of%20the%20country%20and%20felt%20people%20looked%20down%20on%20me.%20I%20only%20speak%20English%2C%20so%20I'm%20sure%20it's%20not%20a%20language%20problem.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20buy%20a%20house%20in%20Bengaluru%20but%20I%20could%20never%20call%20it%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20the%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Bengaluru%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20unplanned%20city%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20country%2C%20one%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20that%20works%20right%20there%2C%20roads%2C%20flyovers%2C%20metros%20all%20in%20a%20chaotic%20loop.%20Obviously%2C%20the%20only%20upside%20of%20living%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20the%20weather.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20comment%20from%20a%20local%20resident%2C%20who%20agreed%20with%20the%20city's%20infrastructure%20struggles%2C%20attributing%20them%20to%20rapid%20but%20unplanned%20growth.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20Bangalorean%2C%20agree%20with%20your%20decision%20to%20leave.%20It's%20a%20smaller%20city%20and%20yes%20rapidly%20developing%20hence%20unplanned%2C%20sorry%20you%20felt%20discriminated.%26quot%3B%20The%20user%20also%20added%20that%20it's%20just%20a%20few%20people%20whose%20actions%20tarnish%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20entire%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20worker's%20experience%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20considering%20a%20number%20of%20factors%20before%20relocating%20for%20a%20job.%20While%20many%20cities%20have%20great%20career%20opportunities%2C%20they%20may%20not%20suit%20everyone's%20preferences%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20need%20to%20weigh%20salary%20hikes%20against%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742456760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F69v47amo_bengaluru-and-noida_625x300_20_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freddit-users-rant-on-moving-to-bengaluru-from-noida-is-viral-says-is-south-indian-7965078%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%2C%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20of%20India%2C%20continues%20to%20attract%20IT%20professionals%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20But%20not%20everyone%20finds%20the%20city%20a%20perfect%20fit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freddit-users-rant-on-moving-to-bengaluru-from-noida-is-viral-says-is-south-indian-7965078%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infosys%20to%20hire%20experienced%20tech%20workers%20across%2040%20skill%20sets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742456741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119247245%2Cimgsize-18328.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Finfosys-lateral-hiring-it-giant-plans-to-recruit-experienced-tech-workers-across-over-40-skill-sets%2Farticleshow%2F119246750.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20is%20hiring%20experienced%20professionals%20across%2040%2B%20skill%20sets%2C%20including%20cloud%20computing%20and%20cyber%20security%2C%20requiring%20at%20least%20two%20years'%20experience%20in%20related%20fields.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Finfosys-lateral-hiring-it-giant-plans-to-recruit-experienced-tech-workers-across-over-40-skill-sets%2Farticleshow%2F119246750.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Implosion%20Or%20Rebellion%3F%20A%20Post-Nitish%20JD(U)%20Will%20Not%20Be%20Pretty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20seeks%20a%20fifth%20term%2C%20question%20marks%20remain%20over%20the%20future%20of%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U).%20Nitish%20faces%20the%20toughest%20political%20battle%20of%20his%20life.%20He%20has%20to%20deftly%20handle%20relationships%20with%20a%20stronger%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%20state%2C%20win%20elections%20due%20in%20Bihar%20in%20six%20months%2C%20and%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20ensure%20a%20bright%20future%20for%20his%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Who%20after%20Nitish'%3F%20The%20chorus%20around%20this%20question%20is%20growing%20in%20Bihar%20and%20the%20JD(U)'s%20circles.%20Will%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20son%20Nishant%20formally%20join%20politics%20and%20be%20named%20as%20his%20successor%3F%20Will%20the%20JD(U)%20disintegrate%20after%20the%20Bihar%20elections%3F%20Will%20it%20formally%20merge%20with%20the%20BJP%3F%20Or%2C%20will%20JD(U)%20leaders%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20and%20other%20parties%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20JD(U)%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20members%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20Bihar.%20Also%2C%20many%20of%20the%20RJD's%20leaders%20joined%20the%20JD(U)%20in%20the%20past%20as%20their%20party%20weakened.%20It's%20a%20common%20joke%20in%20Bihar%20that%20the%20membership%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20is%20complementary%2C%20with%20easy%20to%20and%20fro%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENitish%20Is%20JD(U)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20personality%20cults%20in%20Indian%20politics%3A%20he%20is%20JD(U)%2C%20and%20JD(U)%20is%20him.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20has%20managed%20to%20crush%20all%20competition%20within%20the%20party.%20Years%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20propped%20Sharad%20Yadav%20against%20George%20Fernandes%2C%20and%20then%20dumped%20Yadav%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20parallel%20power%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish's%20earlier%20attempts%20to%20have%20a%20succession%20plan%20have%20failed.%20He%20fell%20out%20with%20political%20strategist%20Prashant%20Kishor%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20even%20made%20the%20party's%20Vice-President%20at%20one%20point%2C%20and%20RCP%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20once%20seen%20as%20Nitish's%20number-two%20in%20the%20party.%20It%20also%20doesn't%20help%20that%20his%20close%20confidantes%2C%20namely%2C%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20Ashok%20Chaudhary%20and%20Sanjay%20Jha%2C%20lack%20charisma%20and%20statewide%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20regional%20parties%20in%20India%20are%20family-controlled.%20This%20acts%20as%20a%20glue%20and%20keeps%20various%20factions%20together.%20Parties%20that%20do%20not%20have%20a%20family%20at%20the%20helm%20or%20a%20clear%20succession%20plan%20are%20today%20facing%20existential%20crises%2C%20like%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20in%20Odisha%2C%20Jayalalitha's%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Awkward%20Question%20About%20Nishant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%2C%20now%20in%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20his%20career%2C%20is%20aware%20that%20the%20party%20needs%20a%20successor%20to%20survive%20after%20him.%20There%20is%20a%20strong%20buzz%20that%20his%20son%20Nishant%20is%20likely%20to%20formally%20join%20politics%20and%20even%20contest%20elections.%20But%20Nishant%20so%20far%20hasn't%20been%20much%20of%20a%20public%20figure.%20His%20first%20major%20appearance%20was%20on%20January%208%2C%20when%20he%20visited%20his%20native%20village%2C%20Kalyan%20Bigha%2C%20with%20his%20father%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20freedom%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20Nishant%20has%20been%20seen%20attending%20party%20meetings%20and%20social%20gatherings%2C%20including%20Holi%20celebrations%2C%20even%20giving%20bytes%20to%20the%20media.%20He%20has%20strongly%20suggested%20that%20the%20NDA%20should%20name%20his%20father%20as%20its%20chief%20ministerial%20face.%20But%20he%20has%20displayed%20a%20visible%20disinclination%20towards%20politics%20in%20the%20past.%20Nitish%20himself%20has%20long%20opposed%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20following%20the%20example%20of%20his%20mentor%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakur%2C%20who%20kept%20his%20family%20away%20from%20politics.%20His%20criticism%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav%20for%20promoting%20family%20members%20in%20politics%20is%20well-known.%20So%2C%20this%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20an%20easy%20decision%20for%20Nitish%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Nishant%20is%20announced%20as%20a%20successor%2C%20he%20could%20face%20opposition%20from%20senior%20leaders%20in%20the%20party.%20The%20JD(U)%20could%20implode%20and%20some%20leaders%20may%20rebel%2C%20turning%20towards%20BJP%2C%20RJD%2C%20or%20even%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20this%20seems%20like%20the%20most%20viable%20option%20for%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20One%20Want%20A%20Rudderless%20Ship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Nishant%20is%20not%20named%20as%20a%20successor%2C%20a%20battle%20could%20break%20out%20amongst%20seniors%20like%20Lallan%20Singh%2C%20Ashok%20Chaudhary%20or%20Sanjay%20Jha%20for%20the%20party's%20control.%20And%20the%20BJP%2C%20sensing%20an%20opportunity%2C%20might%20push%20for%20a%20merger%20to%20strengthen%20its%20base%20in%20the%20state.%20Some%20MLAs%20could%20still%20defect%20to%20other%20parties%2C%20but%20the%20party%20might%20survive%20as%20an%20entity%20at%20least%20with%20Nishant%20at%20the%20helm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiming%20is%20crucial.%20A%20transition%20is%20easier%20when%20a%20party%20is%20in%20power%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20(SP)%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20with%20Lalu's%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20a%20party%20has%20the%20luxury%20of%20quelling%20discontent%20by%20offering%20cabinet%20positions%20to%20disgruntled%20leaders.%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20made%20Akhilesh%20the%20chief%20minister%20after%20his%20party's%20grand%20victory%20in%20the%202012%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20elections.%20Similarly%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%20announced%20Tejashwi%20as%20his%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20won%20the%202015%20elections%20in%20Bihar.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20transferred%20the%20baton%20to%20Rahul%20in%202017%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20out%20of%20power%3B%20the%20move%20had%20ended%20up%20irking%20a%20host%20of%20leaders%2C%20particularly%20the%20%E2%80%98G-23'%20and%20the%20old%20guard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20if%20Nishant%20has%20to%20enter%20politics%2C%20this%20is%20the%20right%20time.%20It%20would%20signal%20to%20senior%20leaders%20who%20the%20boss%20is.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20party%20is%20in%20power%20will%20also%20help%20Nitish%20crush%20a%20possible%20rebellion%20using%20a%20carrot-and-stick%20policy.%20Sure%2C%20Nishant%20may%20face%20challenges%20as%20he%20doesn't%20have%20political%20experience%2C%20but%20the%20move%20could%20prevent%20an%20existential%20implosion%20within%20the%20JD(U)%20after%20Nitish%20calls%20it%20a%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742456700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fp4fmi2ho_nitish-kumar-ani_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fimplosion-or-rebellion-a-post-nitish-jd-u-will-not-be-pretty-7966608%22