ies%20and%20influencers%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20also%20include%20Praneetha%2C%20Nidhi%20Agarwal%2C%20Ananya%20Nagalla%2C%20Siri%20Hanumanthu%2C%20Sreemukhi%2C%20Varshini%20Sounderajan%2C%20Vasanthi%20Krishnan%2C%20Shoba%20Shetty%2C%20Amrutha%20Chowdary%2C%20Nayani%20Pavani%2C%20Neha%20Pathan%2C%20Pandu%2C%20Padhmavathi%2C%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20Vishnu%20Priya%2C%20Harsha%20Sai%2C%20Sunny%20Yadav%2C%20Shyamala%2C%20Tasty%20Teja%2C%20and%20Bandaru%20Sheshayani%20Supritha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20says%20these%20platforms%20promote%20their%20apps%20and%20websites%20through%20social%20media%20advertisements%20with%20the%20help%20of%20celebrities%20and%C2%A0influencers.%20%26quot%3BThousands%20of%20lakhs%20of%20rupees%20are%20involved%20in%20these%20illegal%20platforms%20and%20it%20is%20also%20leading%20many%20families%20into%20distress%2C%20especially%20that%20of%20middle-class%20and%20lower%20middle-class%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20has%20said%20that%20people%20are%20actively%20using%20these%20apps%20and%20many%20have%20lost%20their%20hard-earned%20money.%20He%20has%20said%20he%20too%20was%20about%20to%20deposit%20in%20one%20such%20website%20but%20stepped%20back%20after%20his%20family%20warned%20him.%20The%20complainant%20has%20said%20several%20celebrities%20and%20influencers%20are%20actively%20promoting%20these%20illegal%20betting%20apps%20after%20accepting%20huge%20sums%20as%20and%20remuneration.%20%26quot%3BThese%20platforms%20are%20encouraging%20public%2C%20especially%20people%20that%20are%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20money%2C%20to%20invest%20their%20hard-earned%20and%20family%20money%20into%20those%20apps%2Fwebsites%20and%20slowly%20get%20addicted%20to%20them%2C%20leading%20to%20total%20financial%20collapse%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FIR%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20has%20been%20filed%20under%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20sections%20related%20to%20cheating%20and%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Information%20Techn