ing%20four%20commanding%20victories%20en%20route%20to%20the%20final.%20The%20team%20began%20their%20campaign%20with%20a%20solid%20six-wicket%20win%20over%20Bangladesh%2C%20then%20secured%20a%20convincing%20six-wicket%20triumph%20against%20Pakistan.%20They%20continued%20their%20momentum%20with%20a%2044-run%20victory%20over%20New%20Zealand%20before%20ultimately%20overcoming%20Australia%20by%20four%20wickets%20in%20the%20semi-final%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20press%20release%20from%20BCCI%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoger%20Binny%2C%20President%2C%20BCCI%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWinning%20back-to-back%20ICC%20titles%20is%20special%20and%20this%20reward%20recognises%20Team%20India's%20dedication%20and%20excellence%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20The%20cash%20award%20is%20a%20recognition%20of%20the%20hard%20work%20that%20everyone%20puts%20in%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20This%20was%20also%20our%20second%20ICC%20Trophy%20in%202025%2C%20following%20the%20ICC%20U19%20Women's%20World%20Cup%20triumph%2C%20and%20it%20highlights%20the%20strong%20cricketing%20ecosystem%20in%20place%20in%20our%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevajit%20Saikia%2C%20BCCI%20secretary%2C%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BCCI%20is%20proud%20to%20honour%20the%20players%20and%20support%20staff%20with%20this%20well-deserved%20reward.%20Their%20dominance%20in%20world%20cricket%20is%20a%20result%20of%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20and%20strategic%20execution.%20This%20victory%20has%20justified%20India's%20top%20ranking%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%20and%20we%20are%20sure%20the%20team%20will%20continue%20to%20excel%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%20The%20dedication%20and%20commitment%20shown%20by%20the%20players%20have%20set%20a%20new%20benchmark%2C%20and%20we%20are%20confident%20that%20Indian%20cricket%20will%20keep%20raising%20the%20bar%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742451600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fttmqki9_champions-trophy_6