0Butch%20Wilmore%20-%20286%20days%3A%20Stayed%20aboard%20ISS%20longer%20than%20planned%20(2024-2025)%20due%20to%20propulsion%20issues%20with%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAndrew%20Morgan%20-%20272%20days%3A%20Spent%20272%20days%20on%20ISS%2C%20performing%20seven%20spacewalks%20and%20conducting%20dark%20matter%20research.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Williams%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20the%20most%20cumulative%20spacewalking%20time%20by%20a%20woman%2C%20with%2062%20hours%20and%20six%20minutes%2C%20surpassing%20Peggy%20Whitson's%2060%20hours%20and%2021%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742451420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F6slmqcv_nasa-astronaut-sunita-williams_625x300_19_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-joins-the-top-10-for-longest-single-space-missions-7965215%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA%20astronauts%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore's%20eight-day%20Starliner%20mission%20turned%20into%20a%20286-day%20ISS%20stay%20due%20to%20technical%20failures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsunita-williams-joins-the-top-10-for-longest-single-space-missions-7965215%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lisa%20Ray%20Demands%20Money%20Back%2C%20Air%20India%20Says%20Ticket%20Non-Refundable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-Canadian%20actor%20Lisa%20Ray%20has%2C%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20slammed%20Air%20India%20for%20denying%20a%20medical%20waiver%20for%20a%20ticket%20she%20had%20to%20cancel.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20to%20cancel%20her%20travel%20since%20her%2092-year-old%20father%20was%20unwell%2C%20but%20her%20cancellation%20fee%20was%20not%20waived%20based%20on%20a%20doctor's%20letter.%20The%20Tata-owned%20carrier%20said%20it%20is%20looking%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2052-year-old%20actor%2C%20who%20had%20booked%20her%20ticket%20through%20a%20third-party%20travel%20agent%2C%20shared%20a%20response%20from%20them%20saying%20no%20waiver%20was%20available.%20Airline%20sources%20say%20she%20had%20a%20non-refundable%20ticket%20due%20to%20which%20the%20agent%20had%20refused%20her%20the%20waiver%2C%20and%20not%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%20we%20go%20again%20%40airindia.%20My%20father%20is%2092%2C%20unwell%20and%20I%20have%20to%20cancel%20travel%20due%20to%20his%20ailing%20condition.%20Submitted%20doctors'%20letter%20and%20the%20waiver%20was%20denied%3F%20How%20is%20that%20possible%3F%20Where%20is%20the%20empathy%20from%20an%20airline%20that%20is%20claiming%20to%20care%20about%20passengers%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20Ms%20Ray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20query%2C%20Air%20India%20asked%20Ms%20Ray%20to%20share%20her%20email%20address%20and%20wished%20a%20speedy%20recovery%20to%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDear%20Ms%20Ray%2C%20we%20empathize%20with%20your%20concern%20and%20wish%20your%20father%20a%20speedy%20recovery.%20Please%20help%20us%20with%20the%20email%20address%20from%20which%20you've%20written%20to%20us%20or%20the%20case%20ID%20(if%20any)%20via%20DM.%20We'll%20look%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20suggest%20the%20airline%20had%20offered%20to%20reschedule%20her%20flight%2C%20but%20she%20denied%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ray%2C%20who%20had%20starred%20in%20the%202005%20Hindi%20movie%20%3Cem%3EWater%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20posted%20a%20reply%20from%20her%20travel%20agent%20saying%20no%20medical%20waiver%20was%20available.%20In%20the%20mail%20trail%2C%20Ms%20Ray%20had%20flagged%20her%20father's%20hospitalisation%20and%20said%20that%20she%20had%20attached%20a%20medical%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20aviation%20industry%20works%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20different%20fare%20classes%20-%20fully%20refundable%2C%20non-refundable%2C%20and%20partially%20refundable.%20Based%20on%20which%20fare%20class%20was%20opted%2C%20passengers%20become%20eligible%20for%20a%20refund%20-%20that%20too%20within%20a%20certain%20period%20ahead%20of%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20had%20booked%20the%20ticket%20for%20Rs%205%2C500%2C%20but%20the%20cancellation%20cost%20her%20Rs%204%2C000%2C%20which%20she%20said%20did%20not%20make%20any%20sense.%20Clarifying%20her%20stand%2C%20Ms%20Ray%20said%20it's%20a%20matter%20of%20principle%20and%20not%20money.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20she%20claimed%20she%20was%20provided%20a%20medical%20waiver%20and%20a%20full%20refund%20by%20Emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20case%20of%20a%20legitimate%20medical%20emergency%2C%20most%20airlines%20refund%20the%20amount%20of%20the%20ticket%20after%20providing%20legitimate%20medical%20emergency%20proof%20-%20which%20I%20did%20from%20my%20father's%20neurosurgeon.%20Why%20should%20a%20customer%20be%20penalised%20for%20a%20legitimate%20emergency%20-%20especially%20when%20other%20airlines%20don't%3F%20If%20this%20is%20how%20Air%20India%20treats%20emergencies%2C%20it%20should%20also%20be%20made%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ray's%20criticism%20follows%20a%20list%20of%20high-profile%20passengers%20who%20had%20slammed%20the%20airline%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%20for%20various%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%C2%A0Union%20Agriculture%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-singh-chouhan-slams-air-india-over-broken-seat-ahead-of-farmers-meeting-cheating-passengers-7767756%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20allotted%20a%20%26quot%3Bbroken%26quot%3B%20seat%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20Bhopal%20to%20Delhi.%20When%20he%20questioned%20the%20staff%2C%20he%20was%20told%20the%20management%20had%20been%20informed%20earlier%20about%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20seat%2C%20the%20minister%20had%20alleged.%3C%2