0converted%20into%20a%20'sheesh%20mahal'.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20thought%20that%20he%20was%20the%20'Saddam%20Hussain'%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20that%20he%20would%20remain%20in%20power%20for%2030%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lokesh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20son%20of%20TDP%20leader%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaddam%20Hussein%20was%20Iraq's%20dictator%20and%20ruled%20the%20country%20from%201979%20to%202003.%20His%20administration%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20totalitarian%20and%20the%20Ba'ath%20party%20leader%20is%20held%20responsible%20for%20mass%20killings%20and%20numerous%20other%20acts%20of%20repression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20grandfather%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20my%20father%20is%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20but%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20such%20big%20rooms.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%2C%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20has%20also%20imposed%20penalties%20of%20Rs%20200%20crores%20on%20the%20state%2C%20and%20'sheesh%20mahal'%20was%20built%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lokesh%20said%20the%20YSRCP%20chief%20has%20a%20small%20family%20%26quot%3BHis%20sister%20and%20mother%20have%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20family.%20For%20four%20people%20to%20live%20in%20a%20house%2C%20Rs%20700%20crore%20was%20spent.%20Even%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20doesn't%20have%20such%20a%20big%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20TDP%20government%20will%20take%20a%20call%20on%20what%20to%20do%20with%20the%20palatial%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20late%20YS%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20fell%20out%20with%20his%20sister%20YS%20Sharmila%20over%20her%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20Congress.%20The%20siblings'%20mother%20YS%20Vijayalakshmi%20has%20backed%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20TDP's%20thumping%20win%20and%20retu